description:
Doug finally sees the disaster that is Amazon Prime's War of the Worlds. Is it more than just an Amazon Prime ad? No, and it's amazing. Let's take a look at War of the Worlds (2025).

Join our YouTube Members - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCiH828EtgQjTyNIMH6YiOSw/join

Watch the new Nostalgia Critic - https://youtu.be/2ACHI_DlNyc

Check out our store - https://channelawesome.myshopify.com/

War of the Worlds is a 2025 American screenlife science fiction thriller film based on H. G. Wells's 1898 novel The War of the Worlds. The film was directed by Rich Lee with a screenplay by Kenneth A. Golde and Marc Hyman from a story by Golde. It stars Ice Cube, Eva Longoria, Clark Gregg, Andrea Savage, Henry Hunter Hall, Iman Benson, Devon Bostick, and Michael O'Neill.
